lead_paragraph: - Nico Rosberg, aiming to seize back the championship lead in his home German Formula One Grand Prix, got his weekend off to a strong start by topping the opening practice session on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Rosberg Fastest in Opening German Grand Prix Practice
